			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p20774" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>17</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://amalgrad.ru/viewtopic.php?id=1202#p20774">2008-12-31 12:01:57</a></span></h3>
